---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Dagligdagen" description="Oplev en dag paa Emmerske Efterskole - fra morgenmad til aftensang. Faellesskab, aktiviteter og laering i et trygt miljoee i Toender.">

  <section class="bg-brand-50 py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-4">Dagligdagen paa Emmerske</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Ingen dage er ens, men alle dage er gode. Her er et glimt af, hvad der sker fra morgen til aften.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800 text-center mb-12">En typisk dag</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">07:30</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x2600;&#xFE0F;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Morgenmad</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Faellesspisning i spisesalen</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">08:15</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x1F4D6;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Morgensang</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Vi starter dagen samlet med sang og meddelelser</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">08:30</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x1F4DA;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Undervisning</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Faglige timer med variation og praktiske tilgange</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">12:00</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x1F37D;&#xFE0F;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Frokost</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Varm mad lavet i vores koekken</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">13:00</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x1F3A8;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Valgfag</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Dit eget valg: e-sport, musik, outdoor, kreativt, metal/trae eller sport</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">15:30</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x26BD;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Fri tid</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Sport, hygge, musik eller bare slappe af</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">18:00</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x1F35C;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Aftensmad</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Faelles middag og hygge</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border-2 border-brand-100">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-24 text-center"><span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-xl">19:30</span></div>
          <div class="text-4xl">&#x1F3AE;</div>
          <div><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-800">Aktiviteter</h3><p class="text-gray-600">Spillaften, filmaften, foredrag eller hygge paa stuen</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-brand-50 py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800 text-center mb-12">Se hverdagen</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-200 to-brand-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center p-4">
          <div><div class="text-4xl mb-2">&#x1F3C3;</div><p class="font-semibold">Morgenloeb</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-300 to-brand-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center p-4">
          <div><div class="text-4xl mb-2">&#x1F3A8;</div><p class="font-semibold">Kreativt valgfag</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-400 to-brand-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center p-4">
          <div><div class="text-4xl mb-2">&#x1F3AE;</div><p class="font-semibold">E-sport</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-200 to-brand-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center p-4">
          <div><div class="text-4xl mb-2">&#x1F37D;&#xFE0F;</div><p class="font-semibold">Faellesspisning</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-300 to-brand-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center p-4">
          <div><div class="text-4xl mb-2">&#x1F333;</div><p class="font-semibold">Outdoor</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-400 to-brand-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center p-4">
          <div><div class="text-4xl mb-2">&#x1F3B5;</div><p class="font-semibold">Musik</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mt-6 text-base">Billeder udskiftes med rigtige fotos</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4"><div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-4">Vil du opleve det selv?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">Kom paa besog og foelg en skoledag.</p>
    <a href="/emmerske_clipcore/kontakt" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-700 text-white text-xl font-semibold rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-md">Book besog</a>
  </div></section>

</Layout>